item.title: One person killed, another injured as van hits two-wheeler in Jogulamba Gadwal
item.description:
<![CDATA[One Person Killed Another Injured As Van Hits Two Wheeler In Jogulamba Gadwal
One person killed, another injured as van hits two-wheeler in Jogulamba Gadwal
A man died and a woman was injured after a van collided with their two-wheeler at Beechupally, Jogulamba Gadwal, on Thursday morning. Locals rushed the injured woman to the Government General Hospital for treatment.
By Telangana Today Published Date - 14 August 2025, 01:07 PM
